<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
RED Engineer and Miss Pauling take on the Mecha Spies, RPG-style! </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1gynnx" data-video-descrip="When Craig worries he might turn into Bernard someday, he imagines getting into a fight between him and Kelsey and JP, which is done as a first-generation Pok&amp;Atilde;&amp;Acirc;&amp;copy;mon fight sequence." data-video-title="Craig's Evolution" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1gynnx_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cotc_craigs_evolution.png" data-video-trope="Main/SuddenVideogameMoment" data-video-tropename="Sudden Video-Game Moment" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/CraigOfTheCreekS2E16TheEvolutionOfCraig,WesternAnimation/CraigOfTheCreek" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/cotc_craigs_evolution.png">
<p><span class="bold">Craig's Evolution</span></p>
</a>
